So to fully managed service,

4
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:08,280
as the name indicates,

5
00:00:08,280 --> 00:00:10,860
they will allow you to send email securely,

6
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,840
globally, and at scale.

7
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,940
So the idea is that your application

8
00:00:14,940 --> 00:00:18,540
will use the SES API or SMTP server

9
00:00:18,540 --> 00:00:22,050
and Amazon SES will then send bulk emails to users.

10
