and it gives you a reputation dashboard,

13
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,910
if your emails are open or not,

14
00:00:29,910 --> 00:00:30,930
performance insights,

15
00:00:30,930 --> 00:00:32,880
as well as anti-spam feedback,

16
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:35,430
so if people rates your emails as spam or not.

17
00:00:35,430 --> 00:00:36,810
It provides email statistics

18
00:00:36,810 --> 00:00:40,290
such as deliveries, bounces, feedback loop results,

19
00:00:40,290 --> 00:00:42,300
and whether or not the email was open,

20
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:43,950
and it supports the standard security

21
00:00:43,950 --> 00:00:45,690
for email sending of today,

22
